        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 9. — Calodia makayensis n. sp.,holotype,ZIN,male genitalia:A, genital block (without aedeagus),lateral view;B, pygofer and anal tube,dorsal view;C, genital block (without anal tube, styles shaded), ventral view; D, apex of pygofer lobe, inner side; E, connective and basal part of aedeagus, dorsal view; F, right style, lateral view; G, aedeagus, connective, and style, ventral view; H, aedeagus and connective, lateral view (from right side). Not to scale." ;
